This will be more readable if you use another function to generate the hash
function.

```
if struct_spec.hashable:
  struct_dct['__hash__'] = struct_hasher(struct_spec)
```


```
def struct_hasher(spec):
    def __hash__(self):
        return hash(tuple(getattr(self, f.name) for f in spec.fields))
    return __hash__
```
